8. City:boston is in the middle
9. Movie-Genre:epic is on the far left
10. Birthday:december is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Birthday:july
12. Birthday:azaleamaster == City:rome
13. Movie-Genre:drama == Birthday:april
14. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left or right of Flower:azalea
15. Birthday:december is on the left or right of City:liverpool

